@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">About TaskForge</h2>
            <p>TaskForge is a platform for services, founded by Nicola Stroffolino and George Lefter. It provides a marketplace where users can buy and offer various services, ranging from freelance graphic design to programming assistance and pet grooming services.</p>
            <p>At TaskForge, our mission is to connect service providers with those in need of their expertise, creating opportunities for collaboration and growth.</p>
            <p>We believe in the power of community and strive to build a vibrant ecosystem where individuals can leverage their skills, find support, and achieve their goals.</p>
            <h3 class="mt-5">The Founders</h3>
            <div class="card mb-3 p-3">
                <div class="row g-0">
                    <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="profile-circle">
                            <img src="/img/nicola.stroffolino.png" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="Nicola Profile">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Nicola Stroffolino</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Nicola Stroffolino is not your average programmer. With an innate talent and immense potential, he's a self-taught individual who has mastered the art of coding through sheer determination and passion. However, Nicola's journey has been anything but conventional.</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Known for his larger-than-life personality and a touch of eccentricity, Nicola brings a unique perspective and drive to TaskForge. He's not just in it for the money; he's on a mission to disrupt the service industry and revolutionize the way people access and offer services. Despite his occasional bouts of arrogance, Nicola's unwavering determination and relentless pursuit of excellence make him an invaluable asset to TaskForge.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card p-3">
                <div class="row g-0">
                    <div class="col-md-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                        <div class="profile-circle">
                            <img src="/img/george.lefter.png" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="George Profile">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">George Lefter</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">George Lefter may not be well-versed in the intricacies of programming, but he possesses a unique talent that sets him apart. His strength lies in his exceptional ability to connect with people on a deeper level. George understands their needs, desires, and pain points, allowing him to craft a user experience on TaskForge that is not just functional but empathetic and intuitive.</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Despite being a small entrepreneur, George harbors grand ambitions for TaskForge. He sees beyond the code and algorithms, envisioning a platform that not only offers services but fosters genuine human connections. Driven by his unwavering dedication and fueled by his desire to see his friend's company flourish, George is determined to propel TaskForge to unprecedented heights of success.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
